name: Stabby
summary: Stabby is an intense, multiplayer assassination style game in VR. Players use immersive controls to STAB EVERYTHING. Want to scale buildings and parkour across the city? STAB. Reveal your targets, then drop from rooftops to eliminate them? STAB. Up to 6 players in a lobby can compete to see who’s the best STABBER, with fully articulated avatars they can customize to their liking.
